How much green juice do we drink? This is a two week supply. (About 1-quart/1-liter per person daily)

Fresh juice can last about 4 days in the fridge. When we started this journey it was a weekly ordeal buying the supplies, juicing, & the clean up…which can get discouraging. 
So I came up with a way to make it all at once and not have to juice every four days. 
We freeze the majority of the juice and take it out as we need it to defrost. In the freezer it lasts up to 4-6 months but is rarely in there more than two weeks. We went from juicing weekly to twice a month 🙏🏻. 

DM me with any questions, I’ve got you! 🧃

*our daily consumption of juice is paired with protein & vegetable forward meals🤍
